This project is an extension of HypnoTimeONE.  The application will be 
enhanced with Accelerometer Features.
---
The initial features include:
- Move the center of the HypnosisView relative to the angle the Phone is being tilted.
- Add low-pass filter to reduce 'jerky' feeling when the phone is tilted.
---
July 6, 2011
Updated application to support Shake detection.
When the device is shaken the circular rings will change color.  Note that motion must completely
STOP before an additional shake can trigger a color change.
